quran[4{c,v,t}:
5,42,"yeh jhoot suneney walay aur haraam ke maal khanay walay hain, lehaza agar yeh tumahray paas ( apne muqadmaat le kar ) ayen to tumhe ikhtiyar diya jata hai ke chaho un ka faisla karo warna inkaar kar do inkaar kar do to yeh tumhara kuch bigaar nahi satke, aur faisla karo to phir theek theek insaaf ke sath karo ke Allah insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai"
5,43,aur yeh tumhe kaisay hukum banatay hain jabkay un ke paas Touraat mojood hai jis mein Allah ka hukum likha howa hai aur phir yeh is se mun mourr rahay hain? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh log imaan hi nahi rakhtay
5,44,"hum ne Touraat nazil ki jis mein hadaayat aur roshni thi saaray nabi, jo muslim thay, usi ke mutabiq inn yahodi ban jaane walon ke mamlaat ka faisla karte thay, aur isi terhan Rabbani aur Ahbar bhi ( isi par faisla ka madaar rakhtay thay ) kyunkay inhen kitaab Allah ki hifazat ka zimma daar banaya gaya tha aur woh is par gawah thay pas ( ae giroh yahood! ) tum logon se nah daro balkay mujh se daro aur meri ayaat ko zara zara se muawzay le kar bechna chore do jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi kafir hain"
5,45,"Touraat mein hum ne yahudion par yeh hukum likh diya tha ke jaan ke badlay jaan, aankhh ke badlay aankhh, naak ke badlay naak, kaan ke badlay kaan, daant ke badlay daant, aur tamam zakhamo ke liye barabar ka badla phir jo qisaas ka sadqa kar day to woh is ke liye kaffara hai aur jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi zalim hain"
